header.gameNote: NCAA Women's Championship pres. by Capital One - Alamo Region - Final

videos.headline: Brink fired up early after and-1 bucket
videos.description: Cameron Brink spins inside and scores the basket plus a foul for Stanford.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Brink fired up early after and-1 bucket) 2021/03/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Louisville claims its largest lead after Ahlana Smith steals and scores
videos.description: Ahlana Smith forces a turnover, then lays the ball in right before the half for Louisville.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Louisville claims its largest lead after Ahlana Smith steals and scores) 2021/03/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Russell Wilson on his feet as Stanford claws back into the game
videos.description: Stanford takes its first lead since the first quarter on Kiana Williams' jumper and Russell Wilson is excited.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Russell Wilson on his feet as Stanford claws back into the game) 2021/03/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Prechtel's block, Hull's layup force a Louisville timeout
videos.description: Ashten Prechtel swats Dana Evans' shot, which springs Stanford's transition and leads to Lexie Hull's layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Prechtel's block, Hull's layup force a Louisville timeout) 2021/03/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Anna Wilson hits the big 3 and big brother Russell loves it
videos.description: Anna Wilson's first bucket of the game comes at the right time as she extends Stanford's lead to the delight of her brother, Russell.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Anna Wilson hits the big 3 and big brother Russell loves it) 2021/03/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Stanford erases big deficit to advance to Final Four
videos.description: Stanford trailed by as many as 14 points but stormed back in the second half to knock off Louisville in the women's Elite Eight.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCW Highlight (Stanford erases big deficit to advance to Final Four) 2021/03/30 ESHEET
